data.description: Welcome to this exceptional 35-acre property situated in a serene agricultural zone! Nestled amidst picturesque surroundings, the property boasts stunning views of the majestic Mt Evans, creating an awe-inspiring backdrop for everyday living. The highlight of the property is the immaculate four-bedroom house that has been meticulously maintained. Designed with comfort and functionality in mind, this home offers a welcoming ambiance and ample space for the family. The interior has an array of upgrades, including a brand new on-demand tankless water heater, ensuring a continuous supply of hot water; and a new central vacuum system, providing convenience for keeping the home immaculate. Another fantastic amenity, the home is equipped with a custom reverse osmosis system. With a focus on sustainable living, this estate showcases a range of amenities suitable for agriculture enthusiasts. A livestock pen and hay shelter offer cover for your animals and hay, while the chicken coop offers the opportunity for farm-fresh eggs. The property also features an underground sport dog fence system, granting your four-legged friends the freedom to roam the entire 35 acres while ensuring their safety. One of the unique aspects of this property is its rich history of sustainable land management. For the past 13 yrs, the land has been rotationally browsed by an organic goat dairy herd. This ecologically sound practice has resulted in lush pastures and improved soil quality, making it an ideal setting for those passionate about sustainable farming. Whether you're seeking a tranquil retreat or a working farm, this 35-acre property offers an extraordinary opportunity. With breathtaking views of Mt Evans, modern upgrades, and a host of amenities designed for agricultural pursuits, this estate provides both beauty and functionality. Don't miss the chance to own this remarkable property and embark on a sustainable lifestyle immersed in nature's beauty.
